  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- that went on, after, till March.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you exactly the date, when we were sent to officer courses, those who had the right, which had passed the cadet course and this.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were sent to-- we were sent to Bacau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were check-up, medical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Jews were refused, because, as the Romanian said, something was missing on their weight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In my documents, I was, in faith, in religion, it was written, Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Knowing that, in our school, were no Jews, so automatically, they put Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father was officer in the reserve.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was, more or less, kosher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was sent to-- as a mathematician, I was sent to Craiova, to officer school, artillery.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were officially continuing our studies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took into account that we were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to pass examination, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I returned twice, for examination, from the unit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came on the 27 of June, in the late afternoon, back, already as sort of officer, a warrant officer, the highest rank which was a special intelligence strip we had, that we were officers.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After three months, we would have been permitted to wear the officer uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Russian at the time. 1940, this part was under the Russian, Soviet.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
